{"tid":2447083,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"宅男戀美容妹 手都未拖過 稱保守結婚後方可 2年遭搾乾50萬","createTime":"2021-03-15T03:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T06:12:43.000Z","uid":199670,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3469cc157325d38bc424d2de8f071e5875aad3d5","tid":2447083,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y2YezyIZFlk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY2YezyIZFlk&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDpS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=e49cd61e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y2YezyIZFlk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20180716/YNFO342B4CRG5EM5OVFZEONLKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20180716%2FYNFO342B4CRG5EM5OVFZEONLKE%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDpS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=abe93b34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20180716%2FYNFO342B4CRG5EM5OVFZEONLKE%2F&h=12446ca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20180716/YNFO342B4CRG5EM5OVFZEONLKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n一年零八個月的拍拖生活中，他跟Coco見面不超過十次，而且幾乎每次約會，「表弟」阿杰都在場。<br />\n<br />\n而且雙方從未拖手親嘴，<span class=\"red\">女方稱自己保守，認為結婚後才可拖手親嘴。</span><br />\n<br />\n事實上，阿勇與Coco絕大部分時間，只是透過WhatsApp交流，Coco有時甚至兩、三星期才應機。二人之間的甜言蜜語不多，<span class=\"red\">但阿勇覺得Coco有時關心他「你返咗工未呀」、「加油、努力、返工俾心機」，已令他覺得窩心</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">事後記者採訪女方稱與阿勇只為客戶關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"03551d100919a73a82652328dc1104d997dac142","tid":2447083,"uid":199670,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"毒撚錢真係易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係想blame the victim 但好心啲毒撚啦 用個腦諗下人地會無啦啦中意你啲乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><